Joshua A. Bickel, Columbus Dispatch via USA Today Network via Imagn Content ServicesSlate is making its coronavirus coverage free for all readers.
A red Trump hat on a man at the right of the frame completes the picture.
Joshua A. Bickel: Since the governor started his daily coronavirus briefings, we’ve sent somebody there to livestream the press conference on our Facebook page.
… I think that people responded the way they did because of the emotion, because of the intensity of the picture.
The really nice thing I’ve seen has been people crediting me and the Dispatch, where I work, with the picture, when it’s shared.